column2: Comments: You may include as many comment lines as you like, so long as they are preceded by the COMMENT keyword.
Usage: The first column of each line must begin with a valid keyword.
Keywords: The set of valid keywords are { FAMILY, REV, DATE, COMMENT, BEGIN TRIMOPS, UNIT, HEADER, TRIMOPS, END TRIMOPS }.
Keywords: The minimum valid set and order for keywords is { DATE, REV, BEGIN TRIMOPS, UNIT, HEADER, TRIMOPS, END TRIMOPS }.
Instructions: This file must be saved as a Comma Separated Value (CSV) file for use in test programs.
All numbers are in decimal representation
